@cocktailsbyadam is ready for summer with this full-flavored tropical tipple headlined by a dynamic duo of Denizen Rums! 🌴
.
1 oz @DenizenRum Merchant’s Reserve
½ oz @DenizenRum Vatted Dark
½ oz Fresh Lime Juice
½ oz Fresh Pineapple Juice
½ oz Passionfruit Purée
½ oz Coconut Cream
½ oz Demerara Syrup
2 dashes Aromatic Bitters
3 Fresh Blackberries
.
Add the berries and syrup to a shaking tin and muddle. Pour in the rest of the ingredients, add ice, and whip shake. Strain over crushed ice and garnish with a bouquet of mint, dehydrated lime wheel, and burnt cinnamon.
.
🎵: “2nd Facet” by Hetrik
🎥: @QuachPhotography
📍: @PikePlaceILBistro
💀: @Bottesi.BarTools

At @urbanaanaheim by @Elkaboom
.
@CasaMexicoTequila Blanco
Damiana Liqueur
Passion fruit
Orange cordial
Fresh lime
Red wine float
.
About Urbana
.
Restaurateur Javier Cuadra was raised between Orange County and Michoacan, “the belly” of Mexico.
.
Michoacan boasts an abundance of culture and delectable street foods which influenced Javier into opening a restaurant shacking the region’s finest offerings. “I always had a passion for food, while going to college for international business I worked in the restaurant industry and this inspired me to have my own one day. Experiencing the unique cuisine that Mexico has to offer and seeing how there was nothing like that in Orange County inspired me to bring a small piece of Mexican culture here.” 
.
Javier’s love of “street food” has heavily influenced URBANA’s eclectic menu, which features natural and fresh ingredients including handmade tortillas, gourmet tacos and Red Snapper ceviche, creatively prepared by Chef Ernie Alvarado. “My personal favorite are the Mole enchiladas, made with house made Mole sauce that reminds me of home.” says Javier. Located in the Anaheim Packing House, the candle-lit ambience has earned Golden Foodie Award among other recognitions, “The fact that together with Chef Ernie Alvarado we were able to change how people see Mexican cuisine is a huge accomplishment.”

Special thanks to our friends @zayarum for having TBDE on today. It was fun hanging out and sharing a little bit about how we got started. Appreciate everyone who tuned in. If you are looking to try this drink at home, here’s my recipe!
.
TBDE Painkiller
* 2 ounces Zaya Rum 
* 3 ounces pineapple juice
* 2 oz Fresh Orange Juice
* 1 oz Dorda Coconut Liquer (Cream of Coconut Coco Lopez) 
* Dash of Grated Nutmeg
* Garnish Pineapple (Wedge or Dehydrated Pineapple)

Get fizzy with it. ✨
.
Check out this masterpiece of a summer #cocktail, the “@437 Fizz” by @yellowbellykelly. This drink has everything for a fruity refreshing effect - Vodka, Peach Schnapps, Lemon Juice and more! View the full recipe below. 👇
.
437 FIZZ
1.5oz Vodka
.5oz Peach Schnapps
1oz Pineapple Juice
.75oz Strawberry Hibiscus Simple Syrup
.5oz Fresh Lemon Juice
Add Fresh Mint
Add ice and shake.
Double strain into glass
Top with ice and Strawberry @whiteclaw
Add a splash of Grenadine (optional)
.
Garnish with fresh Mint, Hibiscus and Lemon.
.
🎥  @yellowbellykelly @437

Cheers to #NationalDaquiriDay!
.
Taking it to the Caribbean with “Murder She Wrote” 🍹 by @annie_llew. Mixed with both Smatts Jamaican Rum and Malibu Coconut Rum, this cocktail is sure to turn some heads. See the full list of ingredients below. 👇
.
MURDER SHE WROTE
1oz Smatts Jamaican Rum
.5oz Malibu Coconut Rum
2-3 Dashes of Cocoa Bitters
.75oz Smoked Ginger Syrup
.5oz Lime Juice
.5oz Aquafaba
.
🎥  @annie_llew

.
SPARKLING ITALIAN GREYHOUND
1.5oz Gin or Vodka
2oz Fresh Grapefruit Juice
1oz Campari or Aperol
Sparkling Water
.
Garnish with Marigold Flower.
.
🎥 @join_jules

A #cocktail that takes you on a culinary adventure far away. 🌎
.
Introducing the “Cutting Daru Chai” by @cocktailswith_diego, mixed with Masala Iced Tea, Lemongrass and Ginger Vodka. The garnish of the Cinnamon Stick makes the drink a pure masterpiece. Check out the full list of ingredients below. 👇
.
CUTTING DARU CHAI
60ml Masala Iced Tea or Peach Iced Tea
20 ml Lemongrass & Ginger Vodka @magicmomentsvodka
Top up with Vanilla Whipped Cream 
.
Garnish with Cinnamon and Nutmeg Powder with @officialparleg and Cinnamon Stick.
.
🎥 @cocktailswith_diego
